=Description=

"MakingSociety wiki is a database in progress listing all open hardware companies. It's intended to become a directory of open hardware startups in order to increase their visibility and support the open hardware startup movement.

Criteria:

* company develops hardware products
* products are under an open hardware license
* company is still in activity

(http://wiki.makingsociety.com/index.php5?title=Makingsociety_wiki:Community_portal)


